"How many characters of the filter value to filter against. If set to "
"1, all fields starting with the first letter in the filter value would "
"be matched."
msgstr ""
"Ni herufi ngapi za thamani ya kichujio zitakazotumika kuchuja. Ikiwa "
"itatolewa 1, viwanja vyote vinavyoanza na herufi ya kwanza kwenye "
