"line break, &lt;p&gt; paragraph and &lt;/p&gt; close paragraph tags "
"are inserted automatically. If paragraphs are not recognized simply "
"add a couple of blank lines."
msgstr ""
"Mistari na aya hutambuliwa moja kwa moja. Kovu la mstari la &lt;br "
"/&gt;, &lt;p&gt; aya na lebo za kufunga aya &lt;/p&gt; huingizwa moja "
"kwa moja. Ikiwa aya hazitambuliwi, ongeza tu mistari michache tupu."

