"Content items can be edited using different form modes. Here, you can "
"define which fields are shown and hidden when %type content is edited "
"in each form mode, and define how the field form widgets are displayed "
"in each form mode."
msgstr ""
"Vipengee vya maudhui vinaweza kuhaririwa kwa kutumia aina tofauti za "
"fomu. Hapa, unaweza kufafanua ni maeneo gani yanaonyeshwa na ambayo "
"hayaonyeshwi wakati maudhui ya %type yahaririwa katika kila aina ya "
"fomu, na kufafanua jinsi vidhibiti vya fomu vya maeneo vinaonyeshwa "
"katika kila aina ya fomu."

msgid "Edit %label content type"
msgstr "Hariri aina ya maudhui ya %label"

