"The content has either been modified by another user, or you have "
"already submitted modifications. As a result, your changes cannot be "
"saved."
msgstr ""
"Maudhui yamebadilishwa na mtumiaji mwingine, au tayari umewasilisha "
"mabadiliko. Kwa hivyo, mabadiliko yako hayawezi kuhifadhiwa."

