"Uses a <code>data-align</code> attribute on <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> "
"tags to align images."
msgstr ""
"Inatumia sifa ya <code>data-align</code> kwenye lebo za "
"<code>&lt;img&gt;</code> kuelekeza picha."

