"\n"
"        <p>You can caption images, videos, blockquotes, and so on. "
"Examples:</p>\n"
"        <ul>\n"
"            <li><code>&lt;img src=\"\" "
"data-caption=\"This is a caption\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-caption=\"The Drupal Dance\" "
