"upload sizes (current limit <strong>%limit</strong>)."
msgstr ""
"Weka thamani kama \"512\" (bytes), \"80 KB\" (kilobytes) au \"50 MB\" "
"(megabytes) ili kuweka ukomo wa ukubwa wa faili unaoruhusiwa. Ikiwa "
"utaacha tupu, ukubwa wa faili unaweza kudhibitiwa tu na ukomo wa juu "
"wa PHP kwa post na upakuaji wa faili (ukomo wa sasa "
"<strong>%limit</strong>)."

