"href=\"https://www.php.net/manual/en/image.installation.php\">PHP GD "
"installation documentation</a> if you want to add support."
msgstr ""
"Angalia <a "
"href=\"https://www.php.net/manual/en/image.installation.php\">nyaraka "
"za usakinishaji za PHP GD</a> ikiwa unataka kuongeza msaada."

msgid "@unsupported<br>@ref"
msgstr "@zisizotegemezwa<br>@marejeo"

msgid ""
"The GD Library for PHP is enabled, but was compiled without support "
"for functions used by the rotate and desaturate effects. It was "
"probably compiled using the official GD libraries from the <a "
"href=\"https://libgd.github.io/\">gdLibrary site</a> instead of the GD "
"library bundled with PHP. You should recompile PHP --with-gd using the "
"bundled GD library. See <a "
"href=\"https://www.php.net/manual/book.image.php\">the PHP manual</a>."
msgstr ""
"Maktaba ya GD kwa PHP imewezeshwa, lakini ilikusanywa bila msaada wa "
"vipengele vinavyotumika na athari za kuzungusha (rotate) na kupunguza "
"rangi (desaturate). Huenda ilikusanywa kwa kutumia maktaba rasmi za GD "
"kutoka <a href=\"https://libgd.github.io/\">tovuti ya gdLibrary</a> "
"badala ya maktaba ya GD iliyojumuishwa na PHP. Unapaswa kukusanya upya "
"PHP kwa kutumia chaguo --with-gd ukitumia maktaba ya GD "
"iliyojumuishwa. Angalia <a "
"href=\"https://www.php.net/manual/book.image.php\">mwongozo wa "
"PHP</a>."

msgid "Supported image file format: %formats."
