msgstr "Kuondoa vyombo vya habari."

msgid ""
"These settings apply to the %field field everywhere it is used. Some "
"also impact the way that data is stored and cannot be changed once "
"data has been created."
msgstr ""
"Mipangilio hii inatumika kwa uwanja wa %field kila mahali unapotumika. "
"Baadhi pia huathiri jinsi data inavyohifadhiwa na haiwezi kubadilishwa "
