"Install the <em>Automated Cron</em> module to allow cron execution at "
"the end of a server response."
msgstr ""
"Sakinisha <em>Automated Cron</em> module ili kuwezesha utekelezaji wa "
"cron mwishoni mwa jibu la seva."

