"Text that will be shown when empty elements are included in submission "
"previews and/or emails"
msgstr ""
"Maandishi ambayo yataonyeshwa wakati vipengele vyenye utupu "
"vimejumuishwa katika mwonekano wa awali wa mawasilisho na/au barua "
"pepe"

