"A flexible SASS component to illustrate the steps in a multi-step "
"process e.g. a multi-step form, a timeline or a quiz."
msgstr ""
"Sehemu ya SASS inayobadilika kuonyesha hatua katika mchakato wenye "
"hatua nyingi mfano fomu yenye hatua nyingi, ratiba au jaribio."

