"If checked the computed elements will be hidden from display when the "
"value is an empty string."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa imechaguliwa, vipengele vilivyohesabiwa vitafichwa kutoka kwenye "
"onyesho wakati thamani ni mnyororo tupu."

