msgid ""
"If On (default), Colorbox will add a unique per-request token to the "
"gallery id to avoid images being added manually to galleries. The "
"token was added as a security fix but some see the old behavior as an "
"feature and this settings makes it possible to remove the token."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa Imewashwa (chaguo-msingi), Colorbox itaongeza tokeni ya kipekee "
"kwa kila ombi kwenye kitambulisho cha galari ili kuzuia picha "
"kuongezwa kwa mikono kwenye galaries. Tokeni hii iliongezwa kama "
"marekebisho ya usalama lakini baadhi wanaiona tabia ya zamani kama "
"kipengele, na mipangilio hii inafanya iwezekane kuondoa tokeni hiyo."

