"Updates entity links with <code>data-entity-type</code> and "
"<code>data-entity-uuid</code> attributes to point to the latest entity "
"URL aliases."
msgstr ""
"Inasasisha viungo vya kielekezi vinavyotumia "
"<code>data-entity-type</code> na <code>data-entity-uuid</code> ili "
"kuonyesha anwani za mpya zaidi za viungo vya kielekezi."

