"Kwa chaguo-msingi maelezo huwa yamefichwa, hii itayahakikishia "
"yanaonyeshwa kila mara."

msgid ""
"Allows a user to configure pathauto settings, configure patterns for "
"automated aliases, bulk update and delete URL-aliases."
msgstr ""
"Inamruhusu mtumiaji kusanidi mipangilio ya pathauto, kusanidi mifumo "
