msgstr ""
"Baadhi au matatizo yote yaliyopatikana yanaweza kurekebishwa moja kwa "
"moja kwa kutumia <a href=\":drupal-rector\">drupal-rector</a>. Acha "
"mashine ifanye kazi."

msgid "Fix manually"
msgstr "Rekebisha kwa mkono"

msgid ""
"It looks like there is no automated fixes for either problems found. "
"Check the report for pointers on how to fix."
msgstr ""
"Inaonekana hakuna marekebisho ya moja kwa moja kwa matatizo yoyote "
