msgstr "Mantiki ya masharti (Form API #states) inatumia hali maalum ya %state."

msgid "Conditional logic (Form API #states) is using multiple triggers."
msgstr "Mantiki ya masharti (Form API #states) inatumia vichocheo vingi."

