"Conditional logic (Form API #states) is using multiple nested "
"conditions."
msgstr ""
"Mantiki ya masharti (Form API #states) inatumia masharti mengi "
"yaliyojahirishwa."

msgid "Conditional logic (Form API #states) is using the %operator operator."
msgstr "Mantiki sharti (Form API #states) inatumia kiendeshaji %operator."

