msgstr ""
"Mahitaji yaliyopo chini yanakaguliwa na <a href=\":href\">Ripoti ya "
"Hali</a>."

msgid ""
"If unchecked, all warnings about Webform SPAM protection will be "
"disabled."
msgstr ""
"Kama haitachaguliwa, onyo zote kuhusu ulinzi wa SPAM wa Webform "
"zitasitishwa."

msgid "Check that all entered values for this element are unique."
msgstr ""
"Hakikisha kwamba thamani zote zilizowekwa kwa kipengele hiki ni za "
"kipekee."

msgid ""
"Check that entered values for this element is unique for the current "
"source entity."
msgstr ""
"Thibitisha kwamba thamani zilizowekwa kwa kipengele hiki ni za kipekee "
"kwa chanzo kilichopo sasa."

msgid "Time step"
msgstr "Kipindi cha wakati"

