"You may use tokens. Tokens should use the 'html_date' or "
"'html_datetime' date format. (i.e. @date_format)"
msgstr ""
"Unaweza kutumia tokeni. Tokeni zinapaswa kutumia muundo wa tarehe "
"'html_date' au 'html_datetime'. (kwa mfano @date_format)"

