msgstr ""
"Tuma ukurasa wa awali wakati kitufe cha kurudi cha kivinjari kibonyea "
"kwa fomu zote za wavuti"

msgid "Prepopulation is enabled for all form elements."
msgstr "Kujaza awali kimewezeshwa kwa vipengele vyote vya fomu."

msgid "Please note when an element is hidden it will not be required."
msgstr "Tafadhali kumbuka kuwa wakati kipengele kimefichwa hakitahitajika."

