"Elements contain a duplicate element key %name found on line "
"@line_numbers."
msgid_plural ""
"Elements contain a duplicate element key %name found on lines "
"@line_numbers."
msgstr[0] ""
"Vipengele vina kitufe cha kipengele rudufu %name kilichopatikana "
"kwenye mstari @line_numbers.  \n"
"Vipengele vina vitufe vya vipengele "
"rudufu %name vilivyopatikana kwenye mistari @line_numbers."

msgid "Generate %title submissions"
msgstr "Tengeneza mawasilisho ya %title"

msgid "If checked, this submissions will be starred when reviewing results."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa imechaguliwa, mawasilisho haya yatawekwa nyota wakati wa kupitia "
"matokeo."

msgid ""
"To customize only webform specific elements, you should use the "
"'.webform-submission-form' selector"
msgstr ""
"Ili kubinafsisha vipengele maalum vya fomu ya mtandao pekee, unapaswa "
"kutumia chaguo la '.webform-submission-form'"

msgid "Required indicator is displayed on all forms."
msgstr "Kiashiria kinachotakiwa kinaonyeshwa kwenye fomu zote."

