"If checked, a required elements indicator will be added to this "
"webform."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa imeshikwa alama, kiashiria cha vipengele vinavyohitajika "
"kitaongezwa kwenye fomu hii ya mtandao."

msgid "Autofill with previous submission data"
msgstr "Jaza moja kwa moja na data ya usajili wa awali"

