msgid ""
"If checked, paging, saving of drafts, previews, submissions, and "
"confirmations will not initiate a page refresh on all webforms."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa imechaguliwa, upaginishaji, uhifadhi wa rasimu, onyesho la "
"awali, uwasilishaji, na uthibitisho haviwezi kusababisha kupakia upya "
"ukurasa kwa fomu zote za wavuti."

