msgid "Submission limits and options limits"
msgstr "Mikomo ya uwasilishaji na mikomo ya chaguzi"

msgid "This screencast shows how to set submission limits and options limits."
msgstr ""
"Screencast hii inaonyesha jinsi ya kuweka vizingiti vya uwasilishaji "
"na vizingiti vya chaguo."

