msgstr ""
"Hifadhi kama rasimu kiotomatiki unapotumia ukurasa, kuangalia awali, "
"na wakati kuna makosa ya uthibitisho"

msgid ""
"Automatically save partial submissions when users click the \"Next "
"Page\", \"Previous Page\", or \"Preview\" buttons or when validation "
"errors prevent a webform from being submitted."
msgstr ""
"Hifadhi kwa moja sehemu za fomu zinazotumwa wakati watumiaji "
"wanapobofya vifungo vya \"Ukurasa Ufuatao\", \"Ukurasa wa Awali\", au "
"\"Tazama awali\" au wakati makosa ya uthibitisho yanazuia fomu ya "
"wavuti kuwasilishwa."

