msgstr "Ongeza @item mpya baada ya @item @number"

msgid ""
"If checked, the wizard's progress bar's pages will be hidden or shown "
"based on each pages conditional logic."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa imeshikwa, kurasa za upau wa maendeleo wa mchawi zitasemwa au "
"kuonyeshwa kulingana na mantiki ya masharti ya kila ukurasa."

msgid "Wizard hide all elements label"
msgstr "Jina la kitufe cha kuficha vipengele vyote vya Wizard"

msgid "This is used by the add/remove (+/-) icons."
msgstr "Hii hutumika na alama za kuongeza/kuondoa (+/-)."

