msgid ""
"This screencast walks through how to create faster and better "
"multistep form user experiences using the Webform Cards module."
msgstr ""
"Kirekodi hiki cha skrini kinaonyesha jinsi ya kuunda uzoefu wa "
"watumiaji wa fomu zenye hatua nyingi kwa haraka na bora zaidi kwa "
"kutumia moduli ya Webform Cards."

msgid "Do not track user IP address"
msgstr "Usifuatilie anwani ya IP ya mtumiaji"

