"module</a>."
msgstr ""
"Kuhifadhi rasimu kiotomatiki kunahusu tu kuangalia awali wakati wa "
"kutumia kadi. Tafadhali jaribu kutumia <a href=\":href\">module ya "
"kuhifadhi kiotomatiki ya Fomu ya Mtandao</a>."

msgid ""
"The <strong>Forms</strong> management page lists all available "
"webforms, which can be filtered by the following: keyword (including "
"title, description, elements, user name, or role), category, and "
"status."
msgstr ""
"Ukurasa wa usimamizi wa <strong>Fomu</strong> unaorodhesha fomu zote "
"za mtandao zinazopatikana, ambazo zinaweza kuchujwa kwa yafuatayo: "
"neno kuu (ikiwemo kichwa, maelezo, vipengele, jina la mtumiaji, au "
"jukumu), kategoria, na hali."

msgid ""
"Hiding the %label button can cause unexpected issues. If checked, make "
"sure there is another 'Submit button(s)' element in your form."
msgstr ""
"Kuficha kitufe cha %label kunaweza kusababisha matatizo "
"yasiyotarajiwa. Ikiwa umechagua, hakikisha kuna kiungo kingine cha "
"'Submit button(s)' katika fomu yako."

