"fikiria <a href=\":href_involved\">kujihusisha na jumuiya ya "
"Drupal</a>, <a href=\":href_join\">kujiunga na Ushirika wa Drupal</a>, "
"na <a href=\":href_opencollective\">kuchangia fedha kwenye Open "
"Collective ya moduli ya Webform</a>."

msgid "This behavior is not supported when Ajax is enabled."
msgstr "Tabia hii haitekelezeki wakati Ajax imewezeshwa."

